		<p><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="http://i.creativecommons.org/l/by/4.0/88x31.png" /></a>  This work is licensed under <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" rel="license">Creative Commons Attribution International 4.0</a>. <br />© 2025 Copyright held by the owner/author(s).</p>
			</div>
</section>
		</div>
